    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Under the Minimal profile submission, the seven assessed credibility factors all achieved their required levels. The six unassessed factors represent acknowledged epistemic gaps documented for future resolution. The model is accepted for continued use in the engineering context in which it has been applied, subject to the gap remediation plan. The absence of a structured ContextOfUse object is consistent with the Minimal profile requirements.",
